🇸🇰 Režim „Zvedavého dieťaťa“: Kontrolované učenie
*************************************************
*************************************************
Väčšina LLM sa „učí“ pasívne zo všetkého, čo im príde pod ruku. Môj systém funguje v režime aktívneho dopytovania, kde AI nie je len pasívny prijímač, ale inteligentný filter.

Odmietnutie šumu (Smalltalk Bypass): L3 Bypass okamžite zahadzuje prázdne konverzácie. Systém neplytvá kapacitou na ukladanie nepodstatných dát.

Identifikácia „bielych miest“: AI neustále analyzuje tvoj profil (L0) a hľadá chýbajúce logické prepojenia.

Proaktívne dopytovanie: Namiesto vymýšľania si faktov sa AI pýta: „Mám informáciu A a B, ale chýba mi spojnica C, aby som mohol vykonať akreditáciu. Ako je to?“

Pointa: AI sa neučí zo šumu, ale rastie cez cielené otázky. Výsledkom je vedomostná báza, ktorá neobsahuje balast, ale len čistú, štruktúrovanú pravdu.

************************************************
🇬🇧 Dispute Resolution: Escalation to Parent (L0)
************************************************
In standard AI systems, when a contradiction occurs, the AI either hallucinates or randomly overwrites data. AI-Truth-Scaling does not hide errors; it isolates them.

Disproportionality Detection: As soon as a new piece of information conflicts with an already accredited fact in L0, the system immediately halts the writing process.

Creating a Disputed Record: The information is moved to disputed_records.json. The system doesn't make the choice for you—it identifies and documents the conflict.

L0 Decision Right: The dispute remains "frozen" until the Parent (human) provides a verdict.

The Point: The system would rather admit a contradiction than risk contaminating the knowledge base with unverified data. Data integrity takes precedence over automation.

🇬🇧 "Curious Child" Mode: Controlled Learning
Most LLMs "learn" passively from everything they encounter. My system operates in an active inquiry mode, where the AI is not just a passive receiver, but an intelligent filter.

Noise Rejection (Smalltalk Bypass): The L3 Bypass immediately discards empty conversations. The system does not waste capacity on storing irrelevant data.

Identifying "Blind Spots": The AI constantly analyzes your profile (L0) looking for missing logical connections.

Proactive Inquiry: Instead of inventing facts, the AI asks: "I have information A and B, but I am missing link C to complete the accreditation. What is it?"

The Point: The AI doesn't learn from noise; it grows through targeted questions. The result is a knowledge base free of clutter, containing only pure, structured truth.

